<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>8185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>12859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>比利是山间小学的一个男孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他对其他的男孩儿女孩儿们很刻薄。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22332</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，其他孩子们都叫他坏蛋比利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22333</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看，托尼！那是坏蛋比利。离他远点儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么？他怎么了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34889</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他很刻薄。他很坏。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34890</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>托尼看着比利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>托尼不知道比利为什么是个坏蛋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48281</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，男孩子们在踢足球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48282</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>坏蛋比利跑上前去拿走了球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56674</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们的球在我这儿。哈！哈！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56675</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把我们的球还给我们。你这坏蛋。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61631</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果想要你们的球，跑去捡吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，坏蛋比利把球踢出了围墙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那样真的不好，比利。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，那样不好。这样也不是很好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83482</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>比利把托尼推倒在地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83483</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，坏蛋比利跑开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92515</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“马克，你觉得比利为什么这么坏？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92516</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也不知道。但是，他很刻薄。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>离他远点儿就好。别理他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102821</EndMilliseconds>
